description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene ("Microbe de la peripneumonie" Nocard and Roux 1898; Asterococcus mycoides; Asteromyces peripneumoniae bovis; Borrelomyces peripneumoniae; Bovimyces pleuropneumoniae; Coccobacillus mycoides peripneumoniae; Microbe de la pripneumonie; Micromyces peripneumoniae bovis contagiosae; Mycoplasma peripneumoniae; Pleuropneumonia bovis.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
